AD_TAB.NAME: Custody Details
AD_TAB.HQLWHERECLAUSE: e.id not in ( select e.escmMrequestCustody.id from escm_custody_transaction e join e.escmMaterialReqln as req where req.id=@Escm_Material_Reqln.id@ ) and (( e.id in ( select e.escmMrequestCustody.id from escm_custody_transaction e left join e.goodsShipmentLine as line left join line.shipmentReceipt as req where e.isProcessed='Y' and e.transactiontype='RE' and req.warehouse.id=@Escm_Material_Request.warehouse@ ) and (e.alertStatus='RET' )) or (e.id in ( select e.escmMrequestCustody.id from escm_custody_transaction e where e.isProcessed='Y' and e.transactiontype='RE') and (e.alertStatus='RET' ))) and( e.id in ( select trans.escmMrequestCustody.id from escm_custody_transaction trans,EUT_HijiriDates hijiri where to_date(to_char(hijiri.gregorianDate,'yyyy-MM-dd'),'yyyy-MM-dd') =to_date(to_char(trans.transactionDate,'yyyy-MM-dd'),'yyyy-MM-dd') and ( (substr(hijiri.hijriDate, 1,4)||'-'||substr(hijiri.hijriDate, 5,2)||'-'|| substr(hijiri.hijriDate, 7,2)) <= @Escm_Material_Request.transactionDate@ ) and trans.isProcessed='Y' and trans.returnDate is null )) and e.product.id=@Escm_Material_Reqln.product@

AD_TAB.NAME: Return Custody Detail
AD_TAB.HQLWHERECLAUSE: (e.escmMaterialReqln.id in ( select e.id from Escm_Material_Reqln e join e.escmMaterialRequest req where req.organization .id=@MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.organization@ and req.alertStatus='ESCM_TR' ) or (e.escmMaterialReqln.id is null )) and ((@MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.escmReceivingtype@='INR' and e.alertStatus='IU' and @MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.escmBtype@<>'MA' ) or (@MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.escmBtype@='MA' and e.alertStatus='MA' )) and e.id not in ( select e.escmMrequestCustody.id from escm_custody_transaction e join e.goodsShipmentLine as line join line.shipmentReceipt as req where req.id=@MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.id@ ) and( e.id in ( select trans.escmMrequestCustody.id from escm_custody_transaction trans where trans.transactionDate <= (select inout.movementDate from MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut inout where inout.id = @MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.id@ ) and trans.isProcessed='Y' and trans.returnDate is null ) or (e.escmMaterialReqln.id is null )) and(( e.beneficiaryType = @MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.escmBtype@ and e.beneficiaryIDName.id = @MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.escmBname@ and @MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.escmBtype@<>'MA') or( @MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.escmBtype@='MA' and e.beneficiaryType ='MA') or (e.beneficiaryType is null and e.beneficiaryIDName is null ))

AD_TAB.NAME: Shipment Lines
AD_TAB.HQLWHERECLAUSE: e.escmOrdershipment.id in (select a.escmOrdershipment.id from escm_ordershipment_v a left join a.product b where a.organization.id = @MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.organization@ and a.salesOrder.id =@MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.salesOrder@ and ( ( @MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.escmReceivingtype@='IR' and b is not null and b.productType <> 'S' and b.stocked <> 'N') or ( @MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.escmReceivingtype@='IR' and b is null ) or (@MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.escmReceivingtype@ <> 'IR' and 1=1 ) ))

AD_TAB.NAME: Header
Unified Proposal
AD_TAB.HQLWHERECLAUSE: e.id in ( select b.id from Escm_Proposal_Management b where b.proposalno = (select min(e.proposalno) from Escm_Proposal_Management e where e.escmBidmgmt.id =@ESCM_ProposalEvl_Event.bidNo@) and active ='Y')

AD_TAB.NAME: Add Proposal
AD_TAB.HQLWHERECLAUSE: e.escmBidmgmt.id is null and e.id not in ( select attr.escmProposalmgmt.id from escm_proposal_attr attr where attr.escmProposalevlEvent.id is not null ) and e.proposalstatus='SUB'

AD_TAB.NAME: Order Lines
AD_TAB.HQLWHERECLAUSE: e.salesOrderLine.id in (select a.salesOrderLine.id from Escm_Orderlinereceipt_V a left join a.product b where a.organization.id = @MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.organization@ and a.salesOrderLine.salesOrder.id =@MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.salesOrder@ and ( ( @MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.escmReceivingtype@='IR' and b is not null and b.productType <> 'S' and b.stocked <> 'N') or ( @MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.escmReceivingtype@='IR' and b is null ) or (@MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.escmReceivingtype@ <> 'IR' and 1=1 ) )) and e.summary='N'

AD_TAB.NAME: Related MIR
AD_TAB.HQLWHERECLAUSE: e.relatedMir.id !=@Escm_Material_Request_id@)or (e.id != @Escm_Material_Request_id@ and (e.id = (select m.rEQParent from Escm_Material_Request m where m.id =@Escm_Material_Request_id@) or e.id in (select m1.id from Escm_Material_Request m1 where m1.rEQParent=( select m2.rEQParent from Escm_Material_Request m2 where m2.id =@Escm_Material_Request_id@)) or e.id in (select m2.id from Escm_Material_Request m2 where m2.rEQParent=@Escm_Material_Request_id@)))

AD_TAB.NAME: Site Material Issue Request
AD_TAB.HQLWHERECLAUSE: e.id in (select coalesce(a.id,'') as id from Escm_Material_Request a join a.eUTNextRole r join r.eutNextRoleLineList l where l.role.id=@#AD_Role_ID@ and a.alertStatus <>'DR')and ( e.issiteissuereq in ('Y') ) or (e.id in (select b.escmMaterialRequest.id from Escm_Materialrequest_Hist b where b.updatedBy.id =@AD_User_ID@ and b.role.id=@#AD_Role_ID@ ) and ( e.issiteissuereq in ('Y') )) or ( e.createdBy.id=@AD_User_ID@ and e.role.id = @#AD_Role_ID@ and ( e.issiteissuereq in ('Y') )) or (e.id in (select req.id from Escm_Material_Request req where Exists( select 1 from Eut_Docapp_Delegate dl join dl.eutDocappDelegatelnList dll where dll.userContact.id=@#AD_User_ID@ and dll.role.id = @#AD_Role_ID@ and dll.documentType='EUT_112' and now() between dl.fromDate and dl.date and dl.role.id in ( select li.role.id from Escm_Material_Request re join re.eUTNextRole rl join rl.eutNextRoleLineList li))) and ( e.issiteissuereq in ('Y') )) or ( @ESCM_InventoryAdmin@='Y' and e.issiteissuereq in ('Y') )

AD_TAB.NAME: Contract categories
AD_TAB.HQLWHERECLAUSE: e.escmDeflookupsType.id in (select id from ESCM_DefLookups_Type where reference='POCONCATG') and e.id not in (select contractCategory.id from ESCM_PROD_CONT_CATG where product.id =@Product.id@) and e.active = 'Y'

AD_TAB.NAME: Add Lines
AD_TAB.HQLWHERECLAUSE:
(e.escmMaterialReqln.id in ( select e.id from Escm_Material_Reqln e join e.escmMaterialRequest req where req.organization .id=@MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.organization@ and req.alertStatus='ESCM_TR' ) or (e.escmMaterialReqln.id is null )) and ((@MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.escmReceivingtype@='LD' and e.alertStatus='IU' and @MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.escmBtype@<>'MA' ) or (@MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.escmBtype@='MA' and e.alertStatus='MA' ))
and e.id not in ( select e.escmMrequestCustody.id from escm_custody_transaction e join e.goodsShipmentLine as line join line.shipmentReceipt as req where req.id=@MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.id@ ) and (e.id in ( select trans.escmMrequestCustody.id from escm_custody_transaction trans where trans.transactionDate <= (select inout.movementDate from MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut inout where inout.id = @MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.id@ ) and trans.isProcessed='Y' and trans.returnDate is null )or (e.escmMaterialReqln.id is null ))
and(( e.beneficiaryType = @MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.escmBtype@ and e.beneficiaryIDName.id = @MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.escmBname@ and @MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.escmBtype@<>'MA') or( @MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.escmBtype@='MA' and e.beneficiaryType ='MA'))

AD_TAB.NAME: Header
AD_TAB.HQLWHERECLAUSE:
((( e.id in (select coalesce(a.id,'') as id from Order a join a.eutNextRole r join r.eutNextRoleLineList l where l.role.id=@#AD_Role_ID@ and ((l.userContact is not null and l.userContact.id =@AD_USER_ID@ ) or (l.userContact is null ))) or (e.id in (select b.salesOrder.id from escm_purorderacthist b where b.createdBy.id =@AD_User_ID@ and b.role.id=@#AD_Role_ID@ and b.creationDate=(select max(creationDate) from escm_purorderacthist where salesOrder.id=b.salesOrder.id group by salesOrder.id))) or ( e.id in ( select req.id from Order req join req.eutNextRole rl2 join rl2.eutNextRoleLineList li2 where li2.role.id in (select li.role.id from Order re join re.eutNextRole rl join rl.eutNextRoleLineList li ) and 1=( select 1 from Eut_Docapp_Delegate dl join dl.eutDocappDelegatelnList dll where dll.userContact.id=@#AD_User_ID@ and dll.role.id = @#AD_ROLE_ID@ and dll.documentType='EUT_108' and now() between dl.fromDate and dl.date and dl.role.id in ( select li.role.id from Order re join re.eutNextRole rl join rl.eutNextRoleLineList li ))))
or ( ((e.escmAdRole.id=@#AD_Role_ID@ ) or (e.escmOrdertype in ( select ref.searchKey from EUT_ListAccess lsacc join lsacc.listReference as ref where lsacc.window.id='2ADDCB0DD2BF4F6DB13B21BBCCC3038C' and lsacc.role.id=@AD_Role_Id@ and lsacc.active=true)) or e.escmLegacycontract is not null )
and e.id in ( select e.id from Order e where ((e.escmContactType is not null and ( ((select count(userContact.id) from Eut_User_Lookup_Access where userContact.id=@#AD_User_ID@)>0 and e.escmContactType in ( select usrlook.lookupValues.id from Eut_User_Lookup_Access usrlook where usrlook.userContact.id =@#AD_User_ID@ and usrlook.active=true)) or ((select count(userContact.id) from Eut_User_Lookup_Access where userContact.id=@#AD_User_ID@)=0 and e.escmContactType in ( select look.escmDeflookupsTypeln.id from Eut_Lookup_Access look where look.role.id =@#AD_ROLE_ID@ and look.active=true)))) or(e.escmContactType is null ) ) and( ((e.escmCCity is not null and ((((select count(userContact.id) from EUT_User_Regandcity_Access where userContact.id=@#AD_User_ID@)>0) and ((e.escmCCity.id in ( select usracc.city.id from EUT_User_Regandcity_Access usracc where usracc.userContact.id =@#AD_User_ID@ and usracc.city is not null )) or (e.escmCCity.id in (select id from City where region.id in ( select usrcacc.region.id from EUT_User_Regandcity_Access usrcacc where usrcacc.userContact.id =@#AD_User_ID@ and usrcacc.city is null ) )))) or (((select count(userContact.id) from EUT_User_Regandcity_Access where userContact.id=@#AD_User_ID@)=0) and ((e.escmCCity.id in ( select cityacc.eUTCCity.id from eut_regandcity_access cityacc where cityacc.role.id =@#AD_ROLE_ID@ and cityacc.eUTCCity is not null )) or (e.escmCCity.id in (select id from City where region.id in ( select cityacc.eUTCRegion.id from eut_regandcity_access cityacc where cityacc.role.id =@#AD_ROLE_ID@ and cityacc.eUTCCity is null ) ))))) )or(e.escmCCity is null )))) )) and e.salesTransaction ='N' ) or @ESCM_SCMAdmin@='Y')

AD_TAB.NAME: Partial Counting
AD_TAB.HQLWHERECLAUSE: e.product.id not in(select a.product.id from MaterialMgmtInventoryCountLine a where a.physInventory.id = @MaterialMgmtInventoryCount.id@) and (e.storageBin.id in (select a.id from Locator a where a.warehouse.id=@MaterialMgmtInventoryCount.warehouse@) or e.storageBin.id = null) and ((( select count(pc.id) from escm_usergrp_role rl join rl.escmUsergroups as hdr join hdr.escmUsergrpProcatList as cat join cat.productCategory as pc where rl.role.id = @#AD_Role_ID@ )=0) or (e.product.productCategory IN ( select pc.id from escm_usergrp_role rl join rl.escmUsergroups as hdr join hdr.escmUsergrpProcatList as cat join cat.productCategory as pc where rl.role.id = @#AD_Role_ID@))) and ((true = (select d.escmExcludezero from MaterialMgmtInventoryCount d where d.id= @MaterialMgmtInventoryCount.id@) and e.quantityOnHand > 0 ) or (false =(select d.escmExcludezero from MaterialMgmtInventoryCount d where d.id= @MaterialMgmtInventoryCount.id@)) )

AD_TAB.NAME: Header
Technical Committee Recommendation
AD_TAB.HQLWHERECLAUSE: e.escmTechnicalevlEvent.id is not null and e.escmTechnicalevlEvent.status='CO'

AD_TAB.NAME: Custody Add Line
AD_TAB.HQLWHERECLAUSE: e.beneficiaryType = @MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.escmBtype@ and e.beneficiaryIDName.id = @MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.escmBname@ and (e.alertStatus='IU') and e.id not in ( select e.escmMrequestCustody.id from escm_custody_transaction e join e.goodsShipmentLine as line join line.shipmentReceipt as req where req.id=@MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.id@ ) and (e.id in ( select e.escmMrequestCustody.id from escm_custody_transaction e where to_date(to_char(e.transactionDate,'YYYY-MM-DD'),'YYYY-MM-DD') <= to_date(@MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.escmRefDate@,'YYYY-MM-DD') and e.returnDate is null) or (e.escmMaterialReqln.id is null ))

AD_TAB.NAME: Custody Details
AD_TAB.HQLWHERECLAUSE:
(e.escmMaterialReqln.id in ( select e.id from Escm_Material_Reqln e join e.escmMaterialRequest req where req.organization .id=@MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.organization@ and req.alertStatus='ESCM_TR' ) or (e.escmMaterialReqln.id is null )) and (@MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.escmReceivingtype@='IRT' and e.alertStatus='RET') and e.id not in ( select e.escmMrequestCustody.id from escm_custody_transaction e join e.goodsShipmentLine as line join line.shipmentReceipt as req where req.id=@MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.id@ ) and ( e.id in ( select e.escmMrequestCustody.id from escm_custody_transaction e left join e.goodsShipmentLine as line left join line.shipmentReceipt as req
where e.isProcessed='Y' and e.transactiontype='RE' and req.warehouse.id=@MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.warehouse@ ) or (e.escmMaterialReqln.id is null )) and (e.id in ( select trans.escmMrequestCustody.id from escm_custody_transaction trans,EUT_HijiriDates hijiri where to_date(to_char(hijiri.gregorianDate,'yyyy-MM-dd'),'yyyy-MM-dd')=to_date(to_char(trans.transactionDate,'yyyy-MM-dd'),'yyyy-MM-dd') and ( (substr(hijiri.hijriDate, 1,4)||'-'||substr(hijiri.hijriDate, 5,2)||'-'|| substr(hijiri.hijriDate, 7,2)) <= @MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.movementDate@ ) and trans.isProcessed='Y' and trans.returnDate is null) or (e.escmMaterialReqln.id is null ))

AD_TAB.NAME: Committee Comments
AD_TAB.HQLWHERECLAUSE: e.escmProposalAttr.id in ( select attr.id from escm_proposal_attr attr where attr.escmProposalevlEvent.id in ( select evlev.id from ESCM_ProposalEvl_Event evlev where status='CO'))

AD_TAB.NAME: Lines
AD_TAB.HQLWHERECLAUSE: id not in ( select bid.escmBidmgmt.id from ESCM_AnnouSummaryBid bid ) and e.bidStatus in('ACT')

AD_TAB.NAME: Add Proposal
AD_TAB.HQLWHERECLAUSE: e.id not in (select l.escmProposalmgmt from OrderLine l where escmProposalmgmt is not null ) and (e.proposalstatus = 'AWD' and e.proposalappstatus ='APP') and e.supplier in ( select p.businessPartner from Order p where p.escmOrdertype is not null and p.id =@Order.id@) and (@Order.escmContactType@ is null or e.contractType.id=@Order.escmContactType@) and e.efinBudgetinitial.id = @Order.efinBudgetint@ and e.organization.id=@Order.organization@ and e.version is false

AD_TAB.NAME: Custody Transfer
Material Issue Request
AD_TAB.HQLWHERECLAUSE:
((e.id in (select coalesce(a.id,'') as id from Escm_Material_Request a join a.eUTNextRole r join r.eutNextRoleLineList l where l.role.id=@#AD_Role_ID@ and a.alertStatus <>'DR') and ( e.issiteissuereq not in ('Y') or e.issiteissuereq is null ) or (e.id in (select b.escmMaterialRequest.id from Escm_Materialrequest_Hist b where b.createdBy.id =@AD_User_ID@ and b.role.id=@#AD_Role_ID@ ) and ( e.issiteissuereq not in ('Y') or e.issiteissuereq is null )) or ( e.createdBy.id=@AD_User_ID@ and e.role.id = @#AD_Role_ID@ and ( e.issiteissuereq not in ('Y') or e.issiteissuereq is null )) or (e.id in (
select req.id from Escm_Material_Request req join req.eUTNextRole rl2 join rl2.eutNextRoleLineList li2 where li2.role.id in (select li.role.id from Escm_Material_Request re join re.eUTNextRole rl join rl.eutNextRoleLineList li ) and 1=( select 1 from Eut_Docapp_Delegate dl join dl.eutDocappDelegatelnList dll where dll.userContact.id=@#AD_User_ID@ and dll.role.id = @#AD_ROLE_ID@ and dll.documentType='EUT_112' and now() between dl.fromDate and dl.date and dl.role.id in ( select li.role.id from Escm_Material_Request re join re.eUTNextRole rl join rl.eutNextRoleLineList li )) ) and ( e.issiteissuereq not in ('Y') or e.issiteissuereq is null ))) and e.beneficiaryType in (select ref.searchKey from EUT_ListAccess lsacc join lsacc.listReference as ref where lsacc.window.id='D8BA0A87790B4B67A86A8DF714525736' and lsacc.role.id=@AD_Role_Id@ and lsacc.active=true)) or ( @ESCM_WarehouseKeeper@='Y' and ( e.issiteissuereq not in ('Y') or e.issiteissuereq is null )) or (@ESCM_InventoryAdmin@='Y' and ( e.issiteissuereq not in ('Y') or e.issiteissuereq is null ))

AD_TAB.NAME: Proposal Management
Unified Proposal List
AD_TAB.HQLWHERECLAUSE: e.id in ( select ln.escmProposalmgmt.id from Escm_Proposalmgmt_Line ln where ln.id in ( select up.id from escm_unifiedproposalines_v up where up.escmProposalmgmt.id = @Escm_Proposal_Management.id@) group by ln.escmProposalmgmt.id) and ((select count(ord.id) from Order ord where ord.escmProposalmgmt.id = e.id)=0)

AD_TAB.NAME: Order Line
AD_TAB.HQLWHERECLAUSE: e.salesOrderLine.id in (select a.salesOrderLine.id from escm_orderlineamt_v a left join a.product b where a.organization.id = @MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.organization@ and a.salesOrderLine.salesOrder.id =@MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.salesOrder@ and ( ( @MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.escmReceivingtype@='IR' and b is not null and b.productType <> 'S' and b.stocked <> 'N') or ( @MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.escmReceivingtype@='IR' and b is null ) or (@MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.escmReceivingtype@ <> 'IR' and 1=1 ) ))
